From c7535bafe8a43754b008e6e3f5e85eea0c81db65 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Takagi Tasuku <tasuren@outlook.jp>
Date: Thu, 26 Mar 2026 15:38:35 +0900
Subject: [PATCH 42/49] Add Chromium find-in-page bridge flow

Wire cbf::mojom::CbfProfileService::FindInPage and StopFinding through
CbfBridgeClient into content::WebContents::Find/StopFinding.

Forward results from CbfWebContentsDelegate::FindReply as OnFindReply and
cover search, next/previous, stop, and empty-query no-op behavior in browser tests.
